      • move

        public void move(jig.engine.util.Vector2D dir)
        Initiate animation sequence into specified direction, given by
        Parameters:
        dir - - specifies direction to move The collision sphere of Frogger is automatically moved to the final position. The animation then lags behind by a few seconds(or frames). This resolves the positioning bugs when objects collide during the animation.
